(define/contract (make-the-integer-zero num1 num2)
  (-> exact-integer? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (let loop ((num1 num1) (count 0))
    (if (= num1 0)
        count
        (letrec ((helper (lambda (i)
                           (if (> i 60)
                               -1
                               (let ((result (- num1 (+ (expt 2 i) num2))))
                                 (if (or (= result 0) (< result 0))
                                     (if (= result 0) (add1 count) -1)
                                     (helper (add1 i))))))))
          (helper 0)))))
